title: Uninhibited: A Cuckold Conspiracy
description: Former adult film star Cheyanne Foxx debuts her first novel Uninhibited: A Cuckold Conspiracy. Barry, an executive and husband finds himself swept away in an erotic cuckold mystery. He enlist the aid of close friends to unmask the secret of his wife's innermost desires. Upon doing so, he unleashes hidden treasures within himself.
author: Cheyanne Foxx
